item.title: My First Post
item.description: Introduction This is bold text, and this is emphasized text. Visit the Hugo website! welcome to aditya’s world hey! i’m aditya. if you’re into coding and cool projects, you’re in the right place. i spend most of my time glued to my computer, making tech magic happen. i used to be all about basketball, but these days, my dribbling skills are limited to debugging code. i’m a huge book fan—though let’s be honest, buying books is the real excitement.
